    <item>
      <title>【報價】Nothing 發佈 Headphone (1)，首款 Over-Ear 耳機現身 + 同場發佈 Phone (3)</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/11/nothing-announce-headphone1-phone3-in-hong-kong-with-price-revealed/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=nothing-announce-headphone1-phone3-in-hong-kong-with-price-revealed</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/11/nothing-announce-headphone1-phone3-in-hong-kong-with-price-revealed/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Edward</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Jul 2025 13:30:40 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>手提電話</category>
      <category>流動音樂</category>
      <category>音樂耳機</category>
      <category>Headphone (1)</category>
      <category>Nothing</category>
      <category>Phone (3)</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1316040</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Nothing 這個專門推出「另類」數碼產品的品牌，近年在手機、耳機等各範疇在設計及功能上作出了不少突破，為用家帶來頗多驚喜。今日 Nothing 就宣佈在香港推出旗下首款 Over-Ear 耳機 Headphone (1)，以及新一代旗艦手機 Phone (3)。究竟它們有甚麼特別？就讓 Edward 帶大家到發佈會現場看看吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Headphon (1)：由 KEF 調音外形夠特別&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;首先出場的，肯定是 Nothing 旗下首款罩耳式耳機 Headphone (1)。它的外形貫徹 Nothing 一向劍走偏鋒的破格路線，在市場上耳機及耳罩大多走圓潤設計風格的時候，Headphone (1) 卻採用了長方形的耳機設計，配合圓形的耳罩風格，「天圓地方」的設計確實頗特別。另外，Headphone (1) 耳機機身由耳機機殼到轉動支柄亦採用了不少金屬元素，但耳機背蓋就仍保留了 Nothing 傳統的透明風格，有點重工業風的同時又頗為型格，喜歡潮流時尚的用家應該會頗為喜歡。它亦設有銀、黑兩款選擇，而筆者個人就比較喜歡銀色機款，大家又較喜歡哪個呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1316044 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155052-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155052-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155052.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲這就是 Nothing 最新推出的 Headphone (1)，大家可以見到它採用方形耳機機身設計，十分獨特。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154752-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154752-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154752.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲耳罩就採用傳統圓形設計，「天圓地方」的感覺十分特別。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155104-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155104-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155104.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲類似仿皮物料的耳棉，蓋在雙耳不覺焗促，佩戴感覺算是舒服。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154805-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154805-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154805.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲伸縮頭帶採用塑膠物料製造，彈性十足，而頂部更加入與耳罩相同的仿皮頂墊，加強佩戴時的舒適感。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154800-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154800-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154800.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲耳機機身及支柄均採用金屬物料製造，工業風頗明顯。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316049" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155156-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155156-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_155156.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲頭帶韌度頗高，即使拉開只要不是太過份亦十分硬淨。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154600-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154600-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154600.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲耳機背蓋亦加入了 Nothing 傳統的透明風格設計，貫徹品牌設計理念。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;作為耳機，除了外形，最重要肯定是音質。Headphone (1) 內建了 40mm 動態驅動單元，而且獲得著名音響品牌 KEF 調音，質素應該有一定保證。它亦支援空間音效及頭部追蹤功能，可將任何立體聲音源轉化為 360 度環繞音場，並隨用家動作調整。接駁方面，它支援藍牙無線、USB-C 有線及 3.5mm 有線接駁，藍牙格式方面亦支援 Hi-Res Audio 及 LDAC，更支援最高 24-bit/96kHz 無損傳輸，功能可説十分齊全。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154611-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154611-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154611.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Headphone (1) 內建了 40mm 動態驅動單元，聲底應該不俗。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316054" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162552-694x406.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162552-694x406.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162552.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲官方亦表示 40mm 驅動單元更採用了鍍鎳塗層物料，不但可提供更清晰的高頻聲音，亦可提供豐富有力的低音。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154725-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154725-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154725.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外，耳機亦找來著名音響品牌 KEF 調音，音質應有保證。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162842-694x428.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="428" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162842-694x428.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162842.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲它亦支援空間音效及頭部追蹤功能，可將任何立體聲音效變為 360 度環繞聲效果。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154711-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154711-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154711.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外，它亦支援藍牙無線接駁、USB-C 有線接駁及 3.5mm 有線接駁 3 種接駁模式，可説是市場上接駁方法最齊全的耳機。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162932-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162932-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162932.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外，藍牙無線接駁及 USB-C 有線接駁更可提供最高 24-bit/96kHz 無損傳輸，亦支援 Hi-Res Audio 及 LDAC 格式音效。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另外，作為罩耳式耳機，它亦支援 ANC 主動降噪功能，它每邊耳機均設有兩個前饋及一個反饋，合共 6 個收音咪，配合自家的環境噪音消除系統及結合 AI 技術並經過 2,800 萬種噪音場景訓練，理論上應該有不錯表現。使用時間方面，它可提供長達 35 小時的音樂播放時間，更支援快速充電功能，只需 5 分鐘充電就可提供 2.4 小時開啟 ANC 的額外音樂播放時間。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162712-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162712-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162712.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162801-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162801-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_162801.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外，Nothing Headphone (1) 亦支援 ANC 主動式降噪功能，表現應該不俗。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1316060 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163253-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163253-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163253.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲使用時間方面，官方表示在 ANC 開啟情況下可連續播放 35 小時音樂，而關閉了 ANC 更可播放長達 80 小時音樂，算長氣。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154908-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154908-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154908.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163234-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163234-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163234.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲另外，Headphone (1) 設計上亦有一個特點：耳機上有一個名為 Channel Hop 的實體鍵，配合 Nothing 手機就可以設定一按切換使用中的程式。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Phone (3)：特別小視窗玩味濃&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nothing 亦同場發佈了全新一代的旗艦手機 Phone (3)，它大致維持了上代 Phone (2) 的設計風格，機背依然見到走線的透明設計，不過它最特別的地方，就是今代抽起了過往最獨特的 Glyph 燈效，改為在機背右上角設有一個名為 Glyph Matrix 的微型 LED 熒幕，它不但可以用點陣列形式顯示像時間等資訊，亦內建了一些小遊戲，例如：外出與朋友聚餐時，要找出何人「埋單」時，就可以使用這個小視窗玩超殘酷的「轉酒樽」遊戲。實用性不大但玩味濃。不過它亦有實用之處，就是用家可以指定某些聯絡人連絡自己時，在 Glyph Matrix 上顯示對方點陣列風格的頭像，這個設計令大家在工作繁忙時，也不會錯失重要人物的聯絡，既實用亦體貼。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153323-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153323-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153323.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Nothing 亦同場發佈了新一代旗艦手機 Phone (3)。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153502-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153502-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153502.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲設計風格其實與上代 Phone (2) 差不多，只是 Glyph 燈效不再出現。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316065" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153745-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153745-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153745.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲取而代之的就是這個 Glyph Matrix 小熒幕，它平常可以顯示像時間般的資訊。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153859-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153859-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153859.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154042-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154042-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154042.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲亦可以顯示電量及音量。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316068" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153826-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153826-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153826.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲不過最特別就是內建了少量小遊戲，像上面這款轉酒樽遊戲，要找出何人請食飯或者玩 True or Dare 時使用就最適合了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316070" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163752-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163752-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163752.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲合共有 10 款小遊戲供用家選擇。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1316069 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163630-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163630-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163630.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲用家亦可以指定某些聯絡人連絡自己時，在 Glyph Matrix 上顯示對方點陣列風格的頭像，這個設計令大家在工作繁忙時，也不會錯失重要人物的聯絡，既實用亦體貼。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;規格方面，Nothing Phone (3) 雖然並非採用旗艦級處理器，但也內建了 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8s Gen 4 處理器，亦是香港市場上第二部採用這枚準旗艦級處理器的手機（首部是 Poco F7），表現亦算不錯。此外，它亦內建了 6.67 吋 1.5K 柔性 AMOLED 熒幕，亦是 Nothing 有史以來第一塊這個規格的 AMOLED 熒幕，而且峯值亮度可高達 4500 尼特，相信在日光下亦可清晰看清顯示內容。至於相機方面，Nothing 更首次破天荒在 Phone (3) 上用上 4 個 5,000 萬像素鏡頭，分別是機背的主攝鏡、超廣角鏡及長焦鏡，以及機身前方的自拍鏡，攝力應有一定水準。它亦內建了 5,150mAh 容量電池，官方表示足夠用家使用一整天，它亦支援 65W 有線快充及 15W 無線快充，尤其是使用有線充電，回電速度亦快，即使沒電亦不用太擔心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154106-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154106-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_154106.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲規格方面，Phone (3) 內建了 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8s Gen 4 處理器，是香港市場上第二部採用此處理器的手機。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153414-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153414-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153414.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲熒幕上採用了 6.67 吋 1.5K 柔性 AMOLED 熒幕，亦是 Nothing 有史以來第一塊這個規格的 AMOLED 熒幕，而且峯值亮度可高達 4500 尼特，相信在日光下亦可清晰看清顯示內容。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316073" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153421-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153421-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153421.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153416-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153416-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153416.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲單手操控體驗亦頗為舒服。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153340-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153340-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153340.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲機身右側依然設有 Essential Key。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153839-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153839-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_153839.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316077" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164616-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164616-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164616.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲相機方面，主鏡頭內建了主攝、超廣角及長焦鏡，連同前方的自拍鏡，4 個鏡頭像素均為 5,000 萬。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164852-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164852-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164852.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲電池方面容量為 5,150mAh，足夠用家用上一日以上。它亦支援 65W 有線快充功能，可以在 19 分鐘內將電量由 0% 充至 50%。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316079" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164916-694x405.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="405" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164916-694x405.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_164916.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Nothing Phone (3) 亦支援 IP68 防水防塵功能，使用上令用家十分安心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;兩新品月中推出定價公佈&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;至於開售詳情方面，Nothing Headphone (1) 及 Phone (3) 均會在七月中正式推出，前者推出日期為 7 月 18 日，而後者則為 7 月 15 日。定價方面，Nothing Headphone (1) 為 $2,299。至於手機 Phone (3)，就設有 12 + 256 及 16 + 512 兩個版本，定價分別為 $6,399 及 $6,999，而首購 Nothing 更推出二選一禮遇：用家可付出 12 + 256 版本的成本，免費升級至 16 + 512 版本（價值：$600）；或者選擇 Nothing Ear 真無線耳機（價值：$1,199）作為贈品。而無論選購哪個版本的 Phone (3)，均會獲贈啤酒罐式的酒杯 Nothing Bottle (1) 一個。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163338-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163338-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_163338.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲定價方面，Nothing Headphone (1) 為 $2,299，將會在 7 月 18 日正式開售。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1316081 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_165015-694x401.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="401" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_165015-694x401.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/img_20250710_165015.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲Nothing Phone (3) 則設有 12 + 256 及 16 + 512 兩個規格選擇，定價分別為 $6,399 及 $6,999，而首購期入手 12 + 256 版本更可免費升級至 16 + 512 版本。&lt;/p&gt;
